WEBVTT

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:30.120
if I could change the world tomorrow

00:00:31.040 --> 00:00:33.056
to make it easier for me to navigate,

00:00:33.080 --> 00:00:35.296
the very first thing I would do

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:40.256
is blink and create single stall,
gender-neutral bathrooms

00:00:40.280 --> 00:00:42.936
in all public places.

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:45.720
(Applause)

